@startuml
ATM_WithdrawalMachine
state WaitingForSelection
[*] -> WaitingForSelection: User logs in

state SelectAmount
WaitingForSelection --> SelectAmount: User selects amount from options
SelectAmount --> WaitingForSelection: User confirms selection
SelectAmount --> CustomValue: User chooses to enter custom value

state CustomValue
CustomValue --> Verification: System verifies entered value
Verification --> WaitingForSelection: Valid transaction, proceed
Verification --> Rejected: Transaction rejected, return amount
Rejected --> CustomValue: User re-enters amount

state Rejected
Rejected --> SelectAmount: User selects new amount from options
@enduml
